collection.name: 3Landers
collection.description:
3Landers is a collectible NFT project centered around community, adventure, and collaboration. Each 3Lander resides on the Ethereum blockchain as a unique, non-fungible token (NFT) made up out of a unique combination of traits and underlying “DNAs”. Holding a 3Landers NFT makes you a 3Lander – a member of a world and community that serves to build meaningful long-term connection through collaboration, adventure, building, creating, and dreaming! 

[3L-Biomes](https://opensea.io/collection/3l-biomes)

[3Land Inventory](https://opensea.io/collection/3land-inventory)
